title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: Output parameter is not displaying in the data set dialog
EB: Output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog
SR:
1. Call a stored procedure from an Oracle database
2. Store the query result in an output parameter as an object
3. Open the query result page
4. Verify that the output parameter is not displayed in the data set dialog

Expected result:
- The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog
